title: Five-Year-Old Genius Surprises Ellen DeGeneres with a Trump Burn
text:
Five-Year-Old Genius Surprises Ellen DeGeneres with a Trump Burn 
Too funny. By Kristina Rodulfo Mar 20, 2017 Five-year-old geography whiz Nate Seltzer appeared on The Ellen DeGeneres Show to show off his knowledge of the globe. To everyone's delight, he also proved he has a wicked sense of humor and impressive understanding of current events. While Nate explained a drawing of a world map, Ellen came upon a mysterious figure in what's supposed to be Russia and asks what it is. "It's really funny," Nate whispers,"TRUMP!" He then made this face: Ohhhh! Advertisement   "Why is Trump on Russia?" Ellen asks. Nate keeps it simple, "Because he likes Russia!" It's even funnier because of how he drew Trump: Most Popular
